# NextUp

NextUp is a full-stack task management and productivity platform built with Django (DRF) on the backend and React (Vite) + Tailwind CSS on the frontend. It helps users track tasks and habits, get AI-powered nudges, and visualize their progress over time.

## Features

- **Task management** — create, organize, and track tasks with deadlines
- **Habit presets** — pre-built habit templates backed by a Kaggle dataset
- **AI weekly nudges** — Groq (`llama-3.3-70b-versatile`) powered task suggestions and in-app notifications
- **Analytics** — habit calendar heatmaps and progress visualizations
- **Email reminders** — deadline reminder emails via Gmail SMTP
- **JWT authentication** — SimpleJWT with automatic rotating refresh token handling

## Tech Stack

| Layer     | Technology                               |
| --------- | ---------------------------------------- |
| Backend   | Django, Django REST Framework, SimpleJWT |
| Frontend  | React, Vite, Tailwind CSS                |
| Database  | PostgreSQL                               |
| AI        | Groq API                                 |
| Email     | Gmail SMTP                               |
| Container | Docker, Docker Compose                   |

